{"tid":2336329,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"《電馭叛客2077》超過8MB存檔會損毀且不可修復，官方呼籲減少物品攜帶數量","createTime":"2020-12-22T13:36:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-22T19:31:19.000Z","uid":105567,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c7a9eabd460fd981066ac87ffa9e694bd99f08f6","tid":2336329,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T13:36:12.000Z","msg":"為了玩《電馭叛客 2077》（Cyberpunk 2077）一些小 BUG 可以忍，但在單機遊戲上碰到存檔損毀就不行了。自上週起，海外社群發現到《電馭叛客 2077》存在一個 BUG 會導致存檔損毀並廣為流傳，其原因竟是玩家製作太多物品令存檔超過 8MB 的關係，而這個事實也獲得 CD Projekt Red 證實。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n根據 GOG 問題回報頁面，CDPR 已針對存檔損毀問題作出官方解答，並表示損毀的存檔是無法修復的，建議玩家使用前一個存檔繼續進行遊戲，並呼籲玩家盡量減少身上攜帶的物品數量與製造素材，同時強調若玩家已使用過複製物品的偷吃步（glitch），請重新讀取一個存檔遊玩以面受影響。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://thumbor.4gamers.com.tw/zQqPvm88cYxRblFvYZ-U7g2EZJ8=/filters:watermark(https://img.4gamers.com.tw/default-image/4gamers_watermark_20190925.png,-5,-3,0,17):format(jpeg):quality(90)/https%3A%2F%2Fimg.4gamers.com.tw%2Fpuku-clone-version%2F94cf4a935f28b5944e983fbe172975aa-1ccb02c0fe65a70d8f82b8720e6bae1cfd7f5844.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthumbor.4gamers.com.tw%2FzQqPvm88cYxRblFvYZ-U7g2EZJ8%3D%2Ffilters%3Awatermark%28https%3A%2F%2Fimg.4gamers.com.tw%2Fdefault-image%2F4gamers_watermark_20190925.png%2C-5%2C-3%2C0%2C17%29%3Aformat%28jpeg%29%3Aquality%2890%29%2Fhttps%253A%252F%252Fimg.4gamers.com.tw%252Fpuku-clone-version%252F94cf4a935f28b5944e983fbe172975aa-1ccb02c0fe65a70d8f82b8720e6bae1cfd7f5844.png&h=c2cdb8ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n早在《電馭叛客 2077》上市之初，網路上便有許多關於複製物品的洗錢方法，包含透過專精加成來製作低等物品再拆解販賣等。不過，這樣的方式會導致玩家身上的素材數量增加，也可能因此造成存檔損毀的原因。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\nCDPR 已在上週末進行 1.05 版本更新，針對 PC、PS4、Xbox One 平台修正許多任務 BUG 與最佳化問題，不過裡頭並未提及存檔損毀的修正，而官方強調，未來的更新將會提高存檔容量的上限，但想恢復已損壞的檔案已不可逆。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.4gamers.com.tw/news/detail/46015/crafting-a-huge-number-of-items-can-corrupt-your-cyberpunk-2077-save?fbclid=IwAR3iQcL6HBapZ4kP5A9MpSYNOq_vdVBLvFJILWOq7hIQF4tb8mdRzHQuFqc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.4gamers.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fdetail%2F46015%2Fcrafting-a-huge-number-of-items-can-corrupt-your-cyberpunk-2077-save%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3iQcL6HBapZ4kP5A9MpSYNOq_vdVBLvFJILWOq7hIQF4tb8mdRzHQuFqc&d=OIqfWdBnlTXAQE%2BUUTKEpDbcp9x5SJfJ3tUQBIbvNjo%3D&h=08bfc483\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.4gamers.com.tw/news/detail/46015/crafting-a-huge-number-of-items-can-corrupt-your-cyberpunk-2077-save?fbclid=IwAR3iQcL6HBapZ4kP5A9MpSYNOq_vdVBLvFJILWOq7hIQF4tb8mdRzHQuFqc</a>"},{"pid":"e1e5dd4ffa56e75ae7d45026048117aac5ea6533","tid":2336329,"uid":97240,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T19:31:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://starecat.com/content/wp-content/uploads/what-seems-to-be-the-problem-mary-doctor-it-hurts-when-i-do-this-then-dont-do-that.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstarecat.com%2Fcontent%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fwhat-seems-to-be-the-problem-mary-doctor-it-hurts-when-i-do-this-then-dont-do-that.jpg&h=b0fe4be9&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}